        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Nuclear Power Purchase Agreements Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to develop and carry out a program under which it will enter into one or more long-term (i.e., 10 to 40 years) nuclear power purchase agreements with nuclear reactors that received initial licenses after January 1, 2020.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
